{"tid":1540194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月8 星期日 大家一定要去美國領事館支持美國國會通過(香港人權及民主法案)","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:55:13.000Z","uid":86753,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"144ffba9c773ebe99c3fd2971879d37fee8d95a8","tid":1540194,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭突然退一步都係驚依樣啊 <br />\n仲有未係真正撤回架 <br />\n唔好比佢陰鳩我地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7sCuTUQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7sCuTUQ.jpg&h=45a50004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsT9TUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsT9TUR.jpg&h=2e417f4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72ZpHOc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72ZpHOc.jpg&h=06ccce8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hL8ByUV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhL8ByUV.jpg&h=f0dcbd69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd37545e9df253bb5b1e232364dfea956ddec8cd","tid":1540194,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fcd927bd0f814d00575227b098f42f466f832d","tid":1540194,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"70b8af1ccd358fdc93bf7ed3fa0c45775fd6f182","tid":1540194,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:36.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"bb3b085054a65aa764b123a6558a36990afacdf0","tid":1540194,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:01:48.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"ab364b9bb5c9da0124a04102558aace0fdfae78d","tid":1540194,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:00.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n以後出黎 請帶英文文宣同紙牌<br />\n8/9 請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案集會<br />\n請入908公海link<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FMUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=d9deb923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/MUPPkBeBkY55yqujZTayGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n幫手去twitter做文宣<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=HFtALxS4LzZAkeshXsvvbs4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=dc2caf8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C09QDfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC09QDfB.jpg&h=8c3f1fc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"212988223a66f16d435549b1fb3e94319d3b882c","tid":1540194,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回、學季開始</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、<br />\n六警壓脊椎休克 <span style=\"color: teal;\">至今嚴重昏迷</span>、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案、<br />\n臥底實彈、武警滲透、<span style=\"color: green;\">清朝債主權問題</span><br />\n</span></strong></span>連串<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈</strong></span><span style=\"color: red;\">事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div><br />\n<br />\n#1down4togo<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：\n\n沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者 嫁禍衝擊\n內部分化示威者、\n酷刑凌虐威嚇被捕人士、\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨 阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸、\n假新聞、擺拍、編輯、洗腦文宣製造風向 污名化運動、\n暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑 企圖瓦解前線、\n文宣 抹黑 嫁禍 插贜 示威者、\n暗殺 第一滴血 企圖逆轉民意 國際譴責、\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、\n中立派 賺錢派 政治疲勞、\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、\n白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港、洗腦教育\n\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>這不只是反修例活動<br />\n這是屬於香港人的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流水革命</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"e4a55fa668cc3677df37e1d13dd38597cd82d23d","tid":1540194,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:03.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"32e3ccfe1c4ae91c23f15a91b85e07fe6633ba27","tid":1540194,"uid":194167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37D2uvo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37D2uvo.jpg&h=21720606&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4cfdec4513e851acddce5f6abed24514fafb10f5","tid":1540194,"uid":86753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"fbec148bdd06fa68a65d851c97dec13